verbose_text: This observation together with recorded lower levels of PBL having daily mean value of 811.83 +/- 553.53 m explains the stagnant conditions, which allowed accumulation of higher levels of PM2.5, PM10 and other air pollutants (both non viable aerosols as well as viable -bioaerosols including viruses like as coronaviruses, bacteria, fungi, etc.) at the ground surface air, leading to a higher risk of population exposure.
